  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Travel to The Slopes by Train</h2>
<p>From train tracks to ski tracks, step off and ski on. Enjoy stress-free travel, flexible luggage allowance and room to stretch out. Leave the planning to us and enjoy the journey.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13099593/jungfraubahn-ski-train.jpg" alt="Ski Train" data-udi="umb://media/e4dbc89ec44546d3bea78bddbbbb6946" /></p>
<h2>Tracks to Slopes: Get on Board For a Journey Like No Other</h2>
<p>All aboard a spacious and comfortable journey to the slopes. Swap crowded aisles for scenic tracks. Admire cityscapes, serene lakes and mountains, all while sitting back and enjoying the view from your train window. </p>
<h3>Eurostar Snow Train</h3>
<p>Travelling to France? Your rail journey will start from London St Pancras International Station. With both Standard and Premier Classes on the Eurostar, your comfort and choice are guaranteed.</p>
<p>Stay connected with free WiFi, indulge in onboard refreshments and pack to your hearts content with a generous luggage allowance. Bring more of your wants, not just your needs, and travel in style to your ski destination. Now that's what we call a first-class start to a snowy escape.<a data-udi="umb://document/2bf29261e6e747a98423e8b40c1d21ea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2bf29261e6e747a98423e8b40c1d21ea}" title="Eurostar Snow Train"> Read more about the Eurostar Snow Train</a>.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Our Ski Holidays With Rail Transfers</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Next stop? A ski holiday of a lifetime. Experience an effortless journey when you travel by train to these popular ski resorts. See all the countries and their resorts that you can reach by train for winter 2023/24.</p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__header">Italy </div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><img src="/media/13084102/8580890818_513041ae8f_o.jpg" alt="ski holidays by train" data-udi="umb://media/a33605209ead44b1b6427b276d4033ca" /></p>
<span>With </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887}" title="Sauze d'Oulx">Sauze d’Oulx</a><span> and </span><a data-udi="umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea}" title="Sestriere">Sestriere</a><span> top of the list for Italy, travelling by train to these resorts is a must.</span></div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/574823da33c148cab40b0c300c63ec88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/574823da33c148cab40b0c300c63ec88}" title="Italy ski holidays by rail" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__header">Switzerland</div>
<div class="c-card__header"><img src="/media/13099595/schneesport_ski-und-snowboard_piste_parsenn_06-1.jpg" alt="ski holidays by train" data-udi="umb://media/8a4e6fe40bf841d890392bdc293e1dfd" /></div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><span>With trains arriving at multiple resorts from </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/switzerland/graubunden-ski-region/davos" title="Davos">Davos</a><span> to </span><a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/switzerland/zermatt" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a><span>, viewing the mighty Matterhorn as your wind towards the Swiss Alps is unbeatable.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/bc1bd76cbabc4e7f8eb9be63f059ec2c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bc1bd76cbabc4e7f8eb9be63f059ec2c}" title="Switzerland ski holidays by rail" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__header">Austria </div>
<div class="c-card__header"><img src="/media/13099596/st-anton-400x208-1.jpg" alt="ski holidays by train" data-udi="umb://media/d04a2cbf434a4099ae6c944c912d26b7" /></div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><span>Avid skiers have long been keen to tackle the slopes of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/eb8a4e065fbc4a0fa6a0e0e273886855" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/austria/arlberg-ski-area/st-anton" title="St Anton">St Anton</a><span>. Visit St Anton for your next ski trip and sit back, stretch out your legs and un-wind on the train as you make your way home from an intense week's skiing at this challenging resort. </span></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/52ceff26b77f44c191c54542131586df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52ceff26b77f44c191c54542131586df}" title="Austria ski holidays by rail" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__header">France</div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><img style="width: 356px; height: 191px;" src="/media/13099597/dsc01292-1.jpg?width=356&amp;height=191" alt="ski holidays by train" data-udi="umb://media/79b47bb375ac48779e9667122655a7d2" /></p>
<p><span>With only The Channel between us, France is often the first destination we think of for a ski holiday. Go from London to many French ski resorts by train, including <a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/france/la-rosi%C3%A8re" title="La Rosière">La Rosiere</a>, ideal for families or <a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-resorts/france/tignes-val-d-isere-ski-area/val-disere" title="Val d'Isere">Val d'Isere</a>, great for Après ski seekers. </span></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/e4af3a3602bd41f7bf3e716613b877d9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4af3a3602bd41f7bf3e716613b877d9}" title="France ski holidays by rail" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Be part of the change:</h2>
<p>Our staff and our customers love nature and the great outdoors. The places you visit as part of your Inghams holiday are special, and it’s our responsibility to keep them that way, long into the future. Switching the plane for a train can reduce the carbon footprint of your holiday considerably. We want to make it as easy as possible for our customers to take the train, so we are offering rail travel to 4 countries across Europe. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72" href="/{localLink:umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72}" class="c-btn">Sustainability with Inghams</a></p>
<p><img src="/media/13099193/eurostar-snow-6-838x300.jpg" alt="traintravel" data-udi="umb://media/757d05a8878648b6bff47483a20636cc" /></p>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
